item.title: 【Requests】[REQ VID] - Demi Lovato on CNN's The Fourth of America and NBC's WAWA Welcome America Philly
item.description:
Demi Lovato will have 2 performances today July 4th 2023. They will be a performer in The Fourth of America which will begin 7pm East and will be Broadcasted by CNN, I was reading some comments on the forum and CNN have backhaul and feed (this performance most likely is pre-recorded and there are a bunch of other artists who will be performing as well so i think they will sing just a couple of songs) CNN will rebroadcast this tomorrow as well at 7:30 East i think
and they will be one of the main performers at NBC's WAWA Welcome America in Philadelphia and will broadcast this on NBC Philadelphia News which you can see through Peacock, Roku, Fire Tv and so on; will be a larger setlist, they just soundchecked Confident, Heart Attack, Give Your Heart A Break and Tell Me You Love Me in https://www.nbcphiladelphia.com/ you can stream it as well
Can somebody could record this performances in the highest resolution and upload it here? Either a backhaul, feed or web rip is highly appreciated, sharing is caring
